    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Acreage living within reach of the city.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Pullenvale is the suburb that combines genuine rural-residential lifestyle with a short commute to the Brisbane CBD. Properties sit on land that ranges from 4,000 square metres to several hectares, often surrounded by mature gum trees, with privacy from neighbours and the kind of space that simply does not exist in most parts of Brisbane within a 15 minute drive of the river.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
